title: Selena Gomez looks sweet in baby faced photo as she gives her fans a glimpse of elementary school
text:
Selena Gomez shared a school photo to her Instagram account on Wednesday.

The Wolves singer was looking bright eyed and bushy tailed in a throwback to elementary school when she was about six years old. Though the year is unknown, a baby faced Selena's smile reveals some new teeth growing in on both sides of her mouth.

At age 10 she was already working on the TV show Barney with pal Demi Lovato.

Baby-faced: Selena Gomez shared a school picture to Instagram, looking bright eyed and bushy tailed for a throwback to elementary school

What does it mean: The former Wizards Of Waverly Place star included an ominous caption that read 'We always go into it blindly'; seen in June

Her hair was worn down in a voluminous hairdo, as she flashes a big smile for the camera.

In true 90's-kid fashion, Selena wore a a denim dress over a plain white t-shirt.

The former Wizards Of Waverly Place star included an ominous caption that read, 'We always go into it blindly.'

Since her days on Barney at age 10, the 27-year-old rose to fame in the mid-2000's with appearances on popular TV shows such as Hannah Montana and The Suit Life Of Zach And Cody before getting her own show.

Struggling: Earlier this month, Gomez shared this photo where she looked tired. The caption said, 'Me, all the time.' She has been battling Lupus

She has gone on films like Monte Carlo and producing with 13 Reasons Why and Living Undocumented, both TV shows are on Netflix.

Selena has also become a huge pop star with two studio albums. Her last album was released in 2015. She has since released singles and has been featured on songs by Kygo, Marshmello and Benny Blanco.

Her romantic relationships have also drawn attention over the years, as she had relationships with Nick Jonas, Justin Bieber and The Weeknd.

She sure looks healthy here: The Same Old Love singer put on a smile for her Puma ad

She was recently spotted heading into Niall Horan's home in Los Angeles carrying a bag of groceries, sparking new speculation that the pair were pursuing another chance at love.

Last week Niall shared an Instagram snap from a group dinner where it appeared he had his arm wrapped around her.

Sources told E! that Selena and the One Direction star are 'not dating and have been hanging out as friends' for a while.

A love interest? She was recently spotted heading into Niall Horan's home in Los Angeles carrying a bag of groceries, sparking new speculation that the pair were pursuing another chance at love

'They have always been good friends and have kept in touch throughout the years,' the insider added.

On the night of the group dinner, Selena gave Niall and his new song Nice To Meet Ya a shout-out on her Instagram stories.

Four years earlier the pairing were romantically linked after reportedly putting on a PDA packed display at Jenna Dewan's birthday party.

Is it love or friendship? Last week Niall shared an Instagram snap from a group dinner where it appeared he had his arm wrapped around her
description: Selena Gomez gave a peak in her, short-lived, pre-fame world on Wednesday. The Wolves singer shared a school picture to Instagram, of herself looking bright eyed and bushy tailed.
